fertile crop after scoring their first number one album , the heat is on , the isley brothers ' followed that classic up less than a year later with 1976 's amazing harvest for the world . the band has always had something to say and never have they said more than on the amazing title track . a call for understanding and unity , the song has more relevance today than it did twenty-five years ago . the album is worth it for that song alone , but the rest of the album stands up as well with & quot ; people of today & quot ; , & quot ; let me down easy & quot ; and & quot ; at your best ( you are love ) & quot ; standing out . the album peaked at number nine on the charts